title: #92Noon Friday Feast!
description: PA & Charch are joined by Twins GM Thad Levine to start the show, followed by Chad Greenway midway thru! Cold calls to Twins communications mogul Dustin Morse and Lavelle early in the final hour, and Wild star Eric Staal to wrap the show!
